Source: juju-installer
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ubuntu Developers <ubuntu-devel-discuss@lists.ubuntu.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: juju-installer
Architecture: all
Depends: lxd-installer, python3, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: juju
Description: Wrapper to install and bootstrap Juju on demand
 Installing this package provides a /sbin/juju wrapper that automatically
 installs the Juju snap, initializes LXD, bootstraps a Juju controller,
 and creates a model when the user runs "juju deploy". This enables a
 one-command experience for trying Juju charms on a fresh Ubuntu system.
